					<h2>Introducing SocialSway's <strong>Time Machine</strong></h2>
						<p>Time Machine is the <strong>most advanced</strong> optimized bidding solution in the market. Built on proprietary mathematical and statistical algorithms, Time Machine breaks the traditional process of selecting a bid type based on a campaign objective. Instead, Time Machine calculates the optimal bid <strong>type</strong> and bid <strong>amount</strong> every active hour of a campaign, bidding based on trends and projections. The results: <strong>lower campaign costs-to-goal</strong> (the cost it takes to reach your campaign goal) <strong>and increased campaign performance.</strong></p>
																											
					<hr class="tall">
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-md-7">
							<h4>How It Works</h4>
							<p class="taller">Time Machine learns about the unique, individual aspects of your campaigns, creating a programmatic picture of your brand over time.<br><br>
								As you run campaigns through our platform, Time Machine analyzes your data to predict how your Ad Groups will perform in the near future. This means we know how many impressions, clicks, likes, and actions your Ad Groups will generate, and how your bids will fare, <strong>before</strong> these events actually take place.<br><br>
								We then match up appropriate bid types and amounts for all Ad Groups in all your active campaigns, boosting the bids of Ad Groups that are projected to do well, and lowering the bids of those that arenâ€™t.</p>
						</div>							
						<div class="col-md-5">
							<p><br></p>
							<%= image_tag("Forecasts.jpg", alt: "Sorry the pic didn't load!")%>
						</div>
						
					</div>
					
					
					<hr class="tall">									
