					<hr class="tall">	
					<h4>Boost Performance and Enhance Insights</h4>
													
					<div class="row">	
						<div class="col-md-8">																								
							<p>With Time Machine, brands get a performance boost over current leading optimized bidding solutions. Advertisers will achieve a decrease in total campaign costs-to-goal of up to 20%, as well as a significant reduction in their average CPA. <br><br>
							   Advertisers can see how Time Machine works while their campaigns are running. Predictions for each <br>active Ad Group are updated in <strong>real time</strong>, and advertiers can view a <strong>performance forecast</strong> along with projected bid types and amounts. Advertisers can follow along with Time Machine's logic and enhance <br>their advertising strategies based on this insight. </p>
						</div>																				
						<div class = "col-md-4">
							<ul class="list icons list-unstyled">
								<li><i class="icon icon-money"></i> <strong>Campaign Savings</strong> Save ~20% off the costs to reach your campaign goals.</li>
								<li><i class="icon icon-arrow-down"></i> <strong>Decreased CPA</strong> Lower your average CPA by ~30%.</li>
								<li><i class="icon icon-comment"></i> <strong>Increase Buzz</strong> Increase the amount of interaction (clicks + actions) your campaign recieves when active. </li>
							</ul>								
						</div>				
						
					</div>

					<hr class="tall" />
					<div class="row">
